            {
               "text": "### Introduction\n\nThe *First Steps* section aimed to introduce fundamental concepts from different sciences.\n\nHowever, as Dr. Francisco González A. Redondo points out in various works and lectures, everything we have seen so far is only part of what we can call \"pre-mathematics\" (<htcite0>; <htcite1>; <htcite2>; <htcite3>).\n\nWith everything learned up to this point, reflect:",
